<div class="mdui-typo"><h1 id="polish-vt">polish <strong><em>vt</em></strong></h1>
<p>英 /'pɒlɪʃ/    美 /'pɑːlɪʃ/  </p>
<h2 id="_1">释义</h2>
<h4 id="1">1.★ <strong>磨光；擦亮：</strong></h4>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>polish one’s shoes 
把鞋擦亮</p></div>

<h4 id="2">2.<strong>修改；润色：</strong></h4>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>polish an article 
给文章润色</p></div>

<h2 id="_2">真题解析</h2>
<ol>
<li>Finally, my thanks go to my tutor, who has offered a lot of suggestions and comments on my paper and <strong><em>_</em></strong>_ every page of my draft.   （2012 湖北）<br />
A.approved <br />
B.quoted<br />
C.polished <br />
D.folded  </li>
</ol>
<p>答案：
1. C  </p></div>